org.cpsolver.studentsct.reservation

Class Reservation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.context.AbstractClassWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.reservation.Reservation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Reservation>, AssignmentComparable<Reservation,Request,Enrollment>, CanHoldContext, CanInheritContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>, HasAssignmentContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CourseReservation, CurriculumReservation, DummyReservation, IndividualReservation, OnlineReservation, UniversalOverride

    public abstract class Reservation
extends AbstractClassWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>
implements AssignmentComparable<Reservation,Request,Enrollment>, CanInheritContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>
    Abstract reservation. This abstract class allow some section, courses, and other parts to be reserved to particular group of students. A reservation can be unlimited (any number of students of that particular group can attend a course, section, etc.) or with a limit (only given number of seats is reserved to the students of the particular group).

    Version:
